lzh_formatted:
  title: 寒食
  author: 李婷
  language: lzh
  text: 寒食淸明二月天。東風庭院掛鞦韆。流鶯啼過畫樓去。一樹杏花開政姸。
korean:
  title: 한식
  author: 이정
  language: kor
  text: |-
    한식과 청명의 2월의 하늘
    동쪽 바람 정원에 그네를 매었다
    흐르는 꾀꼬리는 그림 누각을 울면서 지나가는데
    한 나무의 살구꽃은 피어 진정 아름다워라
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_1450_020_0840&viewSync=OT
  footnotes: []
english:
  title: Cold Food Festival
  author: Lee Jeong
  language: eng
  text: |-
    Cold Food and Clear Brightness—the two festivals of the second month's sky.
    East wind hangs the swing in the garden courtyard.
    The flowing nightingale sings past the painted tower,
    And one apricot tree blooms in perfect beauty.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: Cold Food Festival (寒食) and Clear Brightness Festival (清明) are traditional observances occurring in early spring, two days apart in the lunar calendar.
  - key: ''
    value: The 'painted tower' (畫樓) refers to an ornate, decorative building typical of classical Chinese poetry imagery.
